{"id":1004,"date":"2022-02-02T16:26:00","date_gmt":"2022-02-02T16:26:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/?p=1004"},"modified":"2022-02-08T12:56:40","modified_gmt":"2022-02-08T12:56:40","slug":"create-and-delete-logical-volumes","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/?p=1004","title":{"rendered":"Create and delete logical volumes"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>When we have successfully created physical volume and assigned it to a volume group, it&#8217;s time to add this volume group to logical volume. Kinda complicated, I know, but just repeat every steps few times and you are good.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"602\" height=\"343\" src=\"https:\/\/lh4.googleusercontent.com\/m2ojEMHs-NA2xSTamxtL1bc3F25aLCbRsR0uGvrCBV3Z9Q4Ibipl-PDRQqUGEZDqaBl9uoaIrERi3OJRv6TTY--PDercyvpU_GvCm3Mh_9wf4t2Cs6wNHTr0ftvjIYgwaBcIdH0T\"><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Just to remind you where are we exactly in the LVM hierarchy, I will again use this picture.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"create-logical-volume\">Create logical volume<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Let&#8217;s assume we already have volume group created. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"638\" height=\"386\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-236.png?resize=638%2C386&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1005\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-236.png?w=638&amp;ssl=1 638w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-236.png?resize=300%2C182&amp;ssl=1 300w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-236.png?resize=24%2C15&amp;ssl=1 24w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-236.png?resize=36%2C22&amp;ssl=1 36w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-236.png?resize=48%2C29&amp;ssl=1 48w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 638px) 100vw, 638px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>All we have to do now is adding this volume group to the logical volume.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">lvcreate -n name_of_new_logical_volume -L size name_of_volume_group<\/pre>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>And because mine only has 2G I&#8217;ll use only 1 so we can extend it later<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"502\" height=\"57\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-237.png?resize=502%2C57&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1006\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-237.png?w=502&amp;ssl=1 502w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-237.png?resize=300%2C34&amp;ssl=1 300w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-237.png?resize=24%2C3&amp;ssl=1 24w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-237.png?resize=36%2C4&amp;ssl=1 36w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-237.png?resize=48%2C5&amp;ssl=1 48w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 502px) 100vw, 502px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>To display, we surprisingly use <\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">lvdisplay <\/pre>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"612\" height=\"309\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-238.png?resize=612%2C309&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1007\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-238.png?w=612&amp;ssl=1 612w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-238.png?resize=300%2C151&amp;ssl=1 300w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-238.png?resize=24%2C12&amp;ssl=1 24w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-238.png?resize=36%2C18&amp;ssl=1 36w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-238.png?resize=48%2C24&amp;ssl=1 48w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 612px) 100vw, 612px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>At this point we can see it in lsblk as well<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"551\" height=\"266\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-239.png?resize=551%2C266&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1008\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-239.png?w=551&amp;ssl=1 551w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-239.png?resize=300%2C145&amp;ssl=1 300w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-239.png?resize=24%2C12&amp;ssl=1 24w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-239.png?resize=36%2C17&amp;ssl=1 36w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-239.png?resize=48%2C23&amp;ssl=1 48w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 551px) 100vw, 551px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"removing-logical-volume\">Removing logical volume<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">lvremove path_to_logical_volume<\/pre>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"640\" height=\"82\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-240.png?resize=640%2C82&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1009\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-240.png?w=725&amp;ssl=1 725w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-240.png?resize=300%2C38&amp;ssl=1 300w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-240.png?resize=24%2C3&amp;ssl=1 24w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-240.png?resize=36%2C5&amp;ssl=1 36w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-240.png?resize=48%2C6&amp;ssl=1 48w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>We are finally done with creating a LVM hierarchy, now all we have to do is to mount it to some file system, which we will discuss in next post.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>When we have successfully created physical volume and assigned it to a volume group, it&#8217;s [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":982,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"nf_dc_page":"","om_disable_all_campaigns":false,"_mi_skip_tracking":false},"categories":[219],"tags":[263,264,376,377],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/rhsa-configure-local-storage.png?fit=1280%2C720&ssl=1","_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1004"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/index.php?rest_route=%2Fwp%2Fv2%2Fcomments&post=1004"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1004\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1085,"href":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1004\/revisions\/1085"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/media\/982"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/index.php?rest_route=%2Fwp%2Fv2%2Fmedia&parent=1004"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/index.php?rest_route=%2Fwp%2Fv2%2Fcategories&post=1004"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/index.php?rest_route=%2Fwp%2Fv2%2Ftags&post=1004"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}